| `{{ field }}` | `{{ default }}` | {{ desc }} |
{% endfor %}

### `docs:` sub-keys

The `docs:` field accepts three optional sub-keys used to generate README reference tables:

```yaml
docs:
  env:
    ENV_VAR: "Description of this variable"
  volumes:
    /data/path: "Description of this mount"
  ports:
    8080: "Description of this port"
```


